Wii / Xbox 360 / Playstation 3
Mega Man 9 (2008)
Thunder Tornado (Tornado Man Stage)
Ippo Yamada, Ryo Kawakami, Yu Shimoda, Hiroki Isogai & Ogeretsu Kun
